snippet.title: 7 Spirits of Ra gameplay (PC Game, 1987)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for 7 Spirits of Ra, Dos PC game produced by Sir-Tech Software in 1987 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/7-spirits-of-ra/3806/
It is a nice game based on an interesting idea, the Spirits of Ra. You need to find out from the desert pyramids. It is a puzzle game.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.
